<h4>6.2 Error Handling Implemented</h4>
<ul>
    <li><b>What invalid inputs were handled:</b> Addressed looping bugs where text string input skips formatting on cin (used <code>cin.clear()</code> and <code>cin.ignore()</code>).</li>
    <li><b>How negative values were handled:</b> Used <code>if (price &lt; 0 || qty &lt; 0)</code> logic barriers before applying mutation.</li>
    <li><b>How duplicate IDs were handled:</b> Validation check function <code>findIndex(id)</code> runs on Add operation to halt if index found.</li>
    <li><b>How invalid menu choice handled:</b> Switch statement <code>default</code> tag prints an error.</li>
    <li><b>How file errors handled:</b> Safe exit condition during bootstrap via boolean checks utilizing <code>.is_open()</code>.</li>
</ul>

